oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Martha White Biscuit Time - Milton Estes and his Musical Millers - 1947-03-01 - WSM
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WSM program Martha White Biscuit time, originally broadcast on March 1, 1947 at 7:30 pm. Personnel include Louis Buck (announcer), Jimmie Selph (host, performer), Lew Childre (performer), Benny Martin (performer) and the Musical Millers (performers). Sponsored by Martha White. Opening theme music, 'How Many Biscuits Can You Eat'. Milton Estes was out sick, according to information on recording.
